INSERT INTO `blog_post` VALUES (1,'Conagree National Park','conagree-national-park','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Home of Champions</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Astonishing biodiversity exists in Congaree National Park, the largest intact expanse of old growth bottomland hardwood forest remaining in the southeastern United States. Waters from the Congaree and Wateree Rivers sweep through the floodplain, carrying nutrients and sediments that nourish and rejuvenate this ecosystem and support the growth of national and state champion trees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>露营特性：</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>这里的露营（Camping）分为两个地方，</li>\r\n	<li>Longleaf （$10 美刀，离停车场近，百来米）和 Bluff ($5 美刀，离停车场远，0.7 英里）。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>当地小商：</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dollar General（近，卖酒+水+零食的杂货店）；Mr.Bunky（远，卖牛肉+斧头等更大的超市）</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>当地材火（Firewood）：</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>$5美刀买6块木头</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>当地水源：</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>仅限于旅客中心旁，野营地方没有</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>地图：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>发现的小趣事：</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>很多人都没网上预定就野营了，所以等出发的时候再多瞅瞅呗！</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ps.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/cong/planyourvisit/maps.htm\">更多详细资料</a>等</li>\r\n</ul>','2020-08-15 20:51:42.138371','2022-03-17 13:25:47.712356','symbols/mountain-298999_1920.jpg','published','images/logo_fMeJ8SJ_bDMZzgf_3aSqYD5_6gYQIfm_SIIwyHA_xX7YFMM_0aI2qdg_c1i39RR.jpg',12,1,'us national parks','us national parks'),(2,'Biscayne National Park','biscayne-natinal-park','<h3><strong>A Watery Wonderland</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Within sight of Miami, yet worlds away, Biscayne protects a rare combination of aquamarine waters, emerald islands, and fish-bejeweled coral reefs. Evidence of 10,000 years of human history is here too; from prehistoric tribes to shipwrecks, and pineapple farmers to presidents. For many, the park is a boating, fishing, and diving destination, while others enjoy a warm breeze and peaceful scenery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">比斯坎国家公园（</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Biscayne National Park</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">）全年免费开放，但是这个公园大部分都坐落于海上，所以想更好的感受它需要提早预约项目或者自带海上交通工具。其他资料如下：</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">自驾游，导航去<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/dir//Biscayne+National+Park+-+Dante+Fascell+Visitor+Center,+SW+328th+St,+Homestead,+FL/@25.4644095,-80.3698604,13z/data=!4m8!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x88d9e71355c0eb13:0xff6c094c5f9fac58!2m2!1d-80.3347549!2d25.4644137\">旅客中心</a></span></span><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/dir//Biscayne+National+Park+-+Dante+Fascell+Visitor+Center,+SW+328th+St,+Homestead,+FL/@25.4644095,-80.3698604,13z/data=!4m8!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x88d9e71355c0eb13:0xff6c094c5f9fac58!2m2!1d-80.3347549!2d25.4644137\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Dante Fascell Visitor Center</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">（地址：</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">9700 SW 328th ST</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sa