, the beauty of its ancient mountains, and the quality of its remnants of Southern Appalachian mountain culture, this is America&#39;s most visited national park. Plan your visit today!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">自驾游，导航去<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Sugarlands+Visitor+Center/@35.701195,-83.5886446,12z/data=!4m12!1m6!3m5!1s0x885ea8af162d64c7:0xf486c7aee6bde7c2!2sCable+Mill+Visitors+Center!8m2!3d35.5849718!4d-83.8431004!3m4!1s0x8859544509232db1:0xffb628fe14b516ac!8m2!3d35.685675!4d-83.53652\">旅客中心</a></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">大烟山国家公园路况是有一点弯跟陡，导航去的这个是比较接近外面城市的，它附近有很多不同的登山道。它也离</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&ldquo;11</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里的登山道</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Mount Le Conte&rdquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">近。这个登山道前一英里都没什么风景，但是大概走到两英里就能找到比较好的位置看日出</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">+</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">山。不想登山的话，只要沿途开到</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&ldquo;Newdound Gap&rdquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">，停在那附近也能欣赏到那日出的仙境。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">再往里开的话，就能到另外个登山道，可是这个登山道开设时间有限定，平常冬季不开放。喜欢拍拍停停走走看看的话，也推荐去瞅瞅。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">如果你更喜欢开开看看拍拍，那请直接导航去另外个旅客中心。</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">https://www.google.com/maps/place/Cable+Mill+Visitors+Center/@35.5849718,-83.8452891,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x885ea8af162d64c7:0xf486c7aee6bde7c2!8m2!3d35.5849718!4d-83.8431004 </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">这个旅客中心比较偏僻了，途中路线都有地方让你停下欣赏沿途的风景，只是路况会比较弯曲些。如果你是春夏季来，也都会有机会看到野生熊和麋鹿。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">想看日落的话，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Look Rock </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&