\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">发现的小趣事：</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">前往旅客中心的时候，也许你会经过一个很漂亮的地方，有很多童话般的建筑，有坐落在山上的铁路等等；这些是专门给旅客消费的地方，所以拍拍就好。</span></span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">当地的人，它们反而更喜欢去</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Cherokee</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">，如果你喜欢了解印第安人的话。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ps. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">以上资料纯属当时情况，请出发的时候，<a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grsm/contacts.htm\">再次确认</a>。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2020-08-17 00:00:13.864070','2022-03-17 13:15:36.212746','symbols/00000004_cTt4QRq.jpg','published','images/images_yTjSz7n_ij3fl38_jgUiRdz_eQBA495_zgegsQo_ZMxRdVV.jpg',12,1,'us national parks','us national parks'),(5,'Mammoth Cave National Park','mammoth-cave-national-park','<h2><strong>More Than A Cave</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Rolling hills, deep river valleys, and the worlds longest known cave system. Mammoth Cave National Park is home to thousands of years of human history and a rich diversity of plant and animal life, earning it the title of UNESCO World Heritage Site and International Biosphere Reserve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">猛犸象洞国家公园</span></span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">（</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Mammoth Cave National Park</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">）是全年</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&ldquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">免费</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&rdquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">开放，最长的洞穴</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">-</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">长达</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">142</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里。</span></span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">它最大的特色当属与洞穴的特殊形成以及背后的历史故事，比如，制作弹药，开发矿业，研发早期的洞穴之旅项目等等。其他资料如下</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">自驾游，导航去<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Mammoth+Cave+Visitor+Center/@37.186986,-86.1034588,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x886603291b4eb305:0x7ccbaa135646105b!8m2!3d37.1869817!4d-86.1012701\">旅客中心</a></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">，</span></span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">现如今，人们还想参观洞穴的话，我们必须预定</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">ta</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">们的导游项目。如果在旺季时间的话，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">ta</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">们倒是会开放一小部分洞穴可供旅客自由参观。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"f