amily:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">滴水石</span></span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">（</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Dome and Dripstones</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">）：大概两小时，行走于会滴水的洞穴里，有些地段比较窄，但是还是有石阶的。介绍了</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">1920</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">年这所洞穴是如何被发现的，以及它如何形成的。这个旅程在结尾还会顺道去看个钟乳。</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">$15/</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">成人，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">$10/ $9/ 6-12</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">岁的孩童</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">紫罗兰的城市灯笼（</span></span><