-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">景点：</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">化石展览</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Fossil Bone Exihit</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：从收费站进来后，往里开的半途中就能到这。里面展示和介绍了各种在此处发现的生物化石，其中包括，恐龙，早期的海洋生物等等，以及解释了大弯的层次感是如何演化成的。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">平衡之石</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Balanced Rock</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：开去的途中有</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">6</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里是小石头路，加</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">1</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里的更原始的山路（最好四轮驱动车），难后登山，来回大概</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">2.2</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里。适合早、晚去。夏天的中午的话，会太热。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">骡耳之径</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Mule Ears Trail</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：前往圣埃伦娜峡谷的途中，经过</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Mule Ear View point</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">时，如果是春夏季，往</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Mule Ear </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">里开</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">0.5</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里，难后登山，来回</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">3.8</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里的，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">-</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">毛茸茸的山丘。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">龙之屋</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Dragon House Trail</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：比较靠近圣埃伦娜峡谷时，路边停车，来回走</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">0.5</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里，就能看到</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Dragon House</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">（位于左边的），允许人进去参观，从屋内向外望，感官不同的临近景色。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">圣埃伦娜峡谷</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Santa Elena Canyon Trail</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：</span></span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">顺着水泥路</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Ross Maxwell Scenic Drive</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">，前往这的话，中途欣赏到各种经典（龙之屋</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">,</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">骡耳之径，等等）。一路开到底后，顺道走去，路过一个小河流，顺着楼梯道翻过山，就能非常的靠近峡谷山脚。来回路程</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">1.7</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">原始温泉</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Hot spring</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：从</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Hot Spring Historic Exihit Dr.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">开进去，大概</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">1.5</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里石头路。打算去泡温泉的话，先在停车旁的厕所里换好泳衣，过了桥，往左走</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">0.3</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里就能看到。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">身临其境</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Lost Mine Trail</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：中等，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">1700-2100</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">米的海拔；总路程</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">4.8</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里，喜欢动植物</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> + </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">没有高原反应的请走此路。如果走到底的话，也能欣赏到峡谷，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Pine Canyon </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">和</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Juniper Canyon</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">日落之窗</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> The Window</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：中等，看日落的好地点，前往的途中，海拔会从</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">1700</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">米降到</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">200</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">米。从</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Basin </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">露营地出发的话，来回路程</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">4</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里。从旅客中心出发的话，来回路程</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">6</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">巅峰之眼</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Pinnacles Trail</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：中等，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">2100</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">米的海拔，总路程</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">7</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里，从</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Basin</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">旅客中心出发。沿途高出眺望各种山峰。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">一柱擎天</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> Boot Canyon Trail</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">：难，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">2100</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">米的海拔，总路程</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">13</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">英里，从</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Basin</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">旅客中心出发，过了巅峰之眼，往</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><s